    <description>
        <p>Zen is the best way to browse the web. Beautifully designed, privacy-focused, and packed with features. We care about your experience, not your data.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Split view</li>
            <li>Web sidebar</li>
            <li>Tab groups</li>
            <li>Customizable interface</li>
            <li>Vertical Tabs</li>
            <li>And more...</li>
        </ul>
    </description>

